My modification of the Rodinia GPU benchmark (CUDA ONLY) at
https://www.cs.virginia.edu/~skadron/lava/rodinia/downloads.html

1. Patch old code to new CUDA API
2. Bug fixes
3. Most importantly, experiment with various GPU optimization techniques on
these kernels.

Please note that the data is not uploaded with the repo. Please go to the
link above for the data.

Each optimization is done in a single branch, because of the dependency and
compatibility of the changes. There simply is no way that everything is merged
into master.

Current tree:
* 4868d7e (gau_rowblock_fusion) change grid topology to successfully fuse kernels.
* d8d74ac (gau_fusion) unable to naively fuse kernel.
